title: PouBelle Dog Poop Bags - Bright Pink Colour - Super Reliable - Extra Large Strong - Dog Poo Bag - Leak-Proof - Tear Resistant - Scented Dog Waste Bags - Dispenser Compatible - 8 Rolls Refill - 120
features: BRIGHT, BOLD & IMPOSSIBLE TO MISS: PouBelle bright pink dog poo bags are stronger, and bigger than most popular waste bags. Our standout, slightly scented poo bags are easy to spot in grass, mud, sand, anywhere. No more digging around for a dropped poop bag. Whether you're out on a quick street stroll or a countryside adventure, PouBelle dog poo bags are impossible to miss.

WILDLIFE-SAFE COLOUR CHOICE: Not just cute, we’re clever too. Our vibrant pink poo bags send a natural “no thanks” to animals like cows and horses, who don’t associate red or pink with food. That means less wildlife interest and fewer forgotten bags blending into nature. Our dog poo bags are designed with nature in mind and a strong reminder to put your dog waste bags in the bin where they belong.

EXTRA STRONG & LEAK-PROOF: Made for real walks and real mess, PouBelle heavy duty dog poop bags are thick, tear-proof and leak-proof. Whether you’ve got a tiny Terrier or a big bouncy Newfie, these thick dog poo bags are built to handle it - no rips, no stress, no dog poop disasters.

LIGHTLY SCENTED & STINK-PROOF: Nobody needs the whiff of warm poop in their pocket. Our scented dog poo bags help mask the smell and keep things fresh until the next bin drop. Clean-up stays discreet and stress-free, every time.

UNIVERSAL FIT – GRAB, TEAR & GO: PouBelle dog poo bag rolls are made to fit any standard UK dispenser. No faff, no fiddling, just grab a bag, tear it clean, and get on with your walk. Fast, simple, and built for busy dog owners who don’t want to mess around. Even the first poo bag from the roll tears off like a dream with our custom rippable stickers. Stick to Poubelle poubags, we won't let you down.
